{"tid":814812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥：科技人才入境計劃反應不佳","createTime":"2018-09-11T13:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T03:21:48.000Z","uid":54733,"like":112,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"5e13b43723b2070e785834c9486139142a006e76","tid":814812,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T13:39:31.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政府推出科技人才入境計劃，行政長官林鄭月娥表示計劃推行兩個月來反應不佳。<br />\n<br />\n計劃六月起接受申請，機構每聘請三名非本地科技人才便須聘用一名本地全職僱員及兩名本地實習生。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥出席一個創科論壇時透露，計劃反應不佳，機構主要關注聘請海外人才同時須聘用本地人。她呼籲科研公司眼光要看遠一點，幫助整個社會培育人才。<br />\n<br />\n另外，創新科技署上月推出科技專才培訓先導計劃，資助機構聘用博士後專才和本地企業接受高端科技培訓，目前共接到超過120份申請，林鄭月娥形容反應不俗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=319873\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D319873&d=oKeebo5BtbW3C83STe0mjPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=620720d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D319873&h=ee75e295\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=319873</a>"},{"pid":"6690741c9a54d22f1cc2e880c0932bfb56da4ed7","tid":814812,"uid":54733,"like":277,"dislike":3,"score":274,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T13:42:23.000Z","msg":"真正人才都去Microsoft、google、700、阿里巴巴啦<br />\n<br />\n黎香港做垃圾startup咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bed3f4bae53028973f1d9623eb11803c545d9c6","tid":814812,"uid":13303,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T13:43:05.000Z","msg":"支那人都唔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b7ce98a730994b5a8911a6e5680ca31766ea5e","tid":814812,"uid":124983,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T13:44:45.000Z","msg":"你比錢佢地租屋呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b52d5f97ccff3a2a2bae666b1356710c440a67","tid":814812,"uid":37375,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T13:45:26.000Z","msg":"留係香港貪有得住劏房？"},{"pid":"1058b6382cefa87df1eb60edbdfa5029dc8568b9","tid":814812,"uid":34655,"like":96,"dislike":0,"score":96,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T13:48:33.000Z","msg":"我係維尼嘅話輸入150都夠溝淡香港人口啦<br />\n<br />\n點會輸入人才比香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋班真人才點會肯屈就做科學園同數碼港嘅19細公司"},{"pid":"392b857dc8f3b1998266fec5a2c2caeda62daf97","tid":814812,"uid":186177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T13:51:32.000Z","msg":"人地想收兩邊錢做美國果種&ldquo;掛靠H1B&rdquo;公司 邊有錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b7a33a894f8ede8e74138f904393888f2adc8e","tid":814812,"uid":54733,"like":119,"dislike":1,"score":118,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T13:52:01.000Z","msg":"諗起UST化學博士做救護員張圖<br />\n<br />\n香港大把博士畢業嘅人<br />\n<br />\n佢地一係轉行、一係去外地做大嘅科技企業<br />\n<br />\n香港根本唔缺人才，缺嘅係產業"},{"pid":"629fa127943b8f3e3b80df6917103c7e652902e5","tid":814812,"uid":12904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T13:53:24.000Z","msg":"重點係班仆街老細覺得香港人係豬頭骨"},{"pid":"75d7f276305fa38f4ede5bb5cec48b04974e7021","tid":814812,"uid":10692,"like":52,"dislike":3,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T14:01:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c15a6eccf18b580b8b349f8dfaab8c45d24244bd","tid":814812,"uid":35696,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T14:03:03.000Z","msg":"點解唔用呢d錢支持本地IT狗?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e5ded900dfdaf1d1dd23b74c5aed2af6c7d0f1","tid":814812,"uid":3093,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T14:03:24.000Z","msg":"香港而家只會每日輸入150個庸才<br />\n人才邊有份呀"},{"pid":"1b530f281b946bc86f267a3e5ecf57cbc48d51ba","tid":814812,"uid":54733,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"629fa127943b8f3e3b80df6917103c7e652902e5","tid":814812,"uid":12904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T13:53:24.000Z","msg